# HTTPS hostnames the agent VM may reach. Matched against TLS SNI by
# mitmproxy (so SNI-spoofing inside an allowed CONNECT tunnel is caught).
# fnmatch syntax: `*` matches any chars except `.`-style separators in
# Python's fnmatch — i.e. `*.example.com` matches `foo.example.com` but
# NOT `example.com`. List both forms when you want both.
#
# Edit this file then run `./rootcell allow` to hot-reload (no rebuild).

# AWS Bedrock (the agent's LLM provider)
bedrock-runtime.*.amazonaws.com

# OpenAI Codex / ChatGPT Plus-Pro subscription auth
auth.openai.com
chatgpt.com

# GitHub (clones, releases, raw content)
github.com
api.github.com
codeload.github.com
*.githubusercontent.com
objects.githubusercontent.com

# GitLab (mirrors github coverage)
gitlab.com

# Bitbucket
bitbucket.org
*.bitbucket.org

# Azure DevOps (Repos, Pipelines, Artifacts)
dev.azure.com
*.dev.azure.com
ssh.dev.azure.com
*.visualstudio.com

# Nix binary caches and channels
cache.nixos.org
channels.nixos.org
*.cloudfront.net
*.cachix.org

# Language package registries
registry.npmjs.org
*.npmjs.org
pypi.org
files.pythonhosted.org
*.crates.io
proxy.golang.org
sum.golang.org
